{ Welcome to the most important chapter in this book!   The pressure along the a1-h8 diagonal, combined with the pressure on the b-file, is Black's main trump in the Benko. Knowing all tactical ideas connected to the g7-bishop is imperative for the Benko player and will net you a lot of easy points in tournament-play! }
