Kh1 Nf2+ { 23...Bd3  transposes } 5. Kh2 Bd3 6. Qb2 { The most precise is now }
6... Bxc3 { 25...c4  ∓  and   25...Bxb1  ∓  only give a small edge } 7. Bxc3
Qxa2 8. Qxa2 Rxa2
{ Black is winning. He will either take on b1 or d1 and pick up the pawn on b3. }
